WEBVTT

00:01:30.470 --> 00:01:34.840
[The Unclouded Soul]

00:01:35.140 --> 00:01:37.800
[Episode 32]
Support Admin Watch on
kissasia.cam or kisskh.org

00:01:38.870 --> 00:01:40.400
So your reckless flattery

00:01:40.420 --> 00:01:42.080
finally got you into trouble.

00:01:47.590 --> 00:01:48.400
It's alright. It's alright.

00:01:48.400 --> 00:01:49.840
I'm not really angry.

00:01:49.840 --> 00:01:51.200
You're quite cute actually,

00:01:51.200 --> 00:01:51.950
much better than

00:01:51.950 --> 00:01:53.680
that snide Ao Hen.

00:01:54.280 --> 00:01:54.840
Xiao Yao,

00:01:55.280 --> 00:01:56.880
did Ao Hen provoke you again?

00:01:57.789 --> 00:01:58.759
No, no, no.

00:01:58.759 --> 00:01:59.820
My spiritual power

00:01:59.920 --> 00:02:01.590
is too weak.

00:02:01.640 --> 00:02:03.150
It has nothing to do with Senior.

00:02:03.150 --> 00:02:04.040
It doesn't matter.

00:02:04.040 --> 00:02:05.150
As long as we are here,

00:02:05.150 --> 00:02:06.760
you are still unmatched in this world.

00:02:06.760 --> 00:02:07.230
Yes.

00:02:08.770 --> 00:02:10.000
I appreciate your kindness,

00:02:10.000 --> 00:02:12.530
but I think it's better
to cultivate on my own.

00:02:13.630 --> 00:02:14.400
Sister,

00:02:14.870 --> 00:02:16.280
let me teach you instead.

00:02:17.800 --> 00:02:18.430
Um,

00:02:18.910 --> 00:02:21.170
could you please stop calling me Sister?

00:02:22.560 --> 00:02:23.760
You said it yourself.

00:02:24.079 --> 00:02:24.630
If I don't

00:02:24.750 --> 00:02:26.150
call you Sister anymore,

00:02:26.280 --> 00:02:27.280
does that mean

00:02:27.280 --> 00:02:28.300
I can like you?

00:02:29.030 --> 00:02:31.079
What nonsense are you talking about?

00:02:31.079 --> 00:02:32.680
If anyone is teaching her, it will be me.

00:02:32.680 --> 00:02:34.120
Since when was it your turn?

00:02:34.120 --> 00:02:34.750
Qiong Qi,

00:02:35.000 --> 00:02:36.590
you can barely protect yourself,

00:02:36.590 --> 00:02:38.510
and you still have the nerve
to teach Xiao Yao.

00:02:38.510 --> 00:02:39.840
You're courting death.

00:02:41.560 --> 00:02:43.750
If Xiao Yao wishes to recover
her former spiritual power,

00:02:43.750 --> 00:02:45.280
then naturally I will be
the one to teach her.

00:02:45.280 --> 00:02:45.840
Fine.

00:02:46.190 --> 00:02:47.470
Get past me first before you say that.

00:02:47.470 --> 00:02:49.280
-Fine.
-I was the one who said it first.

00:02:49.280 --> 00:02:50.079
It has nothing to do with you.

00:02:50.079 --> 00:02:51.120
It has nothing to do with you.

00:02:51.120 --> 00:02:52.030
It has nothing to do with me?

00:02:52.030 --> 00:02:54.560
-I said it has nothing to do with you.
-Enough!

00:02:55.590 --> 00:02:56.860
If you three are too idle,

00:02:56.860 --> 00:02:58.780
then help us rebuild Demons' Valley.

00:02:58.780 --> 00:03:01.110
At least put that strength
of yours to use.

00:03:01.750 --> 00:03:03.810
I am not meant to handle menial tasks.

00:03:04.400 --> 00:03:05.200
Wouldn't that

00:03:05.750 --> 00:03:07.150
be a waste of my talents?

00:03:07.710 --> 00:03:10.000
But many places were destroyed by you.

00:03:11.400 --> 00:03:13.490
If you are unwilling to stay and help,

00:03:13.560 --> 00:03:14.710
please leave.

00:03:17.190 --> 00:03:18.430
Sister,

00:03:18.430 --> 00:03:19.290
don't be angry.

00:03:19.680 --> 00:03:21.030
I'll do whatever you ask me to.

00:03:21.030 --> 00:03:23.520
Can you stop calling me
"Sister" all the time?

00:03:23.520 --> 00:03:25.360
How old do you think
you are compared to me, anyway?

00:03:25.360 --> 00:03:26.150
My Lord!

00:03:28.470 --> 00:03:29.190
My Lord!

00:03:31.310 --> 00:03:33.710
Qiong Qi, Ao Hen, and Teng She

00:03:33.710 --> 00:03:36.030
are all repairing the barriers
throughout the valley.

00:03:36.030 --> 00:03:37.079
That's good.

00:03:37.520 --> 00:03:40.110
We don't have to rely solely on
your power anymore.

00:03:40.110 --> 00:03:41.340
I was worried

00:03:41.560 --> 00:03:43.910
that while you
were repairing the barriers,

00:03:43.910 --> 00:03:45.470
those three might launch a sneak attack,

00:03:45.470 --> 00:03:47.200
and we wouldn't know what to do.

00:03:47.360 --> 00:03:49.090
It seems I worried for nothing.

00:03:49.390 --> 00:03:50.240
Now things

00:03:50.280 --> 00:03:51.610
are finally evened out.

00:03:52.550 --> 00:03:54.010
But come to think of it,

00:03:54.190 --> 00:03:55.850
Xiao Yao is truly remarkable.

00:03:56.150 --> 00:03:58.360
She managed to make those
three fierce and ruthless beings

00:03:58.360 --> 00:03:59.490
obey her every word.

00:04:00.590 --> 00:04:01.910
I wonder

00:04:01.910 --> 00:04:03.280
what kind of tangled karma or bond

00:04:03.280 --> 00:04:05.080
the four of them shared

00:04:05.080 --> 00:04:06.910
ten thousand years ago.

00:04:08.030 --> 00:04:08.560
My Lord,

00:04:08.630 --> 00:04:09.120
I...

00:04:15.770 --> 00:04:18.800
The three old monsters have been
sealed away for ten thousand years.

00:04:18.800 --> 00:04:20.000
How could they possibly be a match

00:04:20.000 --> 00:04:20.950
for Your Lordship,

00:04:20.950 --> 00:04:23.350
who cultivates day and night without rest?

00:04:25.800 --> 00:04:27.200
When all is said and done,

00:04:27.450 --> 00:04:29.180
all of this is Xiao Yao's fault.

00:04:29.750 --> 00:04:30.750
Somehow she

00:04:31.000 --> 00:04:33.000
became entangled with those three.

00:04:33.040 --> 00:04:36.040
A hundred years ago,
she already betrayed your trust.

00:04:36.480 --> 00:04:37.220
And now,

00:04:37.630 --> 00:04:39.440
seeing their great power

00:04:39.830 --> 00:04:41.630
and how they obey her every word,

00:04:41.860 --> 00:04:43.000
she's playing both sides

00:04:43.000 --> 00:04:43.990
like the fickle woman she is.

00:04:43.990 --> 00:04:44.580
Silence!

00:04:45.740 --> 00:04:47.640
Xiao Yao doesn't even recognize them.

00:04:47.640 --> 00:04:48.960
How can you blame her?

00:04:51.210 --> 00:04:52.670
If it weren't for Xiao Yao,

00:04:53.070 --> 00:04:54.000
this calamity

00:04:54.510 --> 00:04:56.710
wouldn't have been resolved so easily.

00:04:57.800 --> 00:04:59.680
If I say something nice, it's wrong.

00:04:59.680 --> 00:05:02.010
If I say something harsh, it's also wrong.

00:05:02.310 --> 00:05:04.440
Your thoughts are truly hard to guess.

00:05:36.140 --> 00:05:37.740
I guess this is what they mean

00:05:37.960 --> 00:05:41.230
by "handsome as a jade tree
in the breeze."

00:05:42.770 --> 00:05:43.820
I'm so cultured!

00:06:08.030 --> 00:06:08.860
Senior,

00:06:08.960 --> 00:06:11.430
you've worked so hard
repairing the barrier.

00:06:11.430 --> 00:06:12.430
Try this.

00:06:13.800 --> 00:06:14.820
What's this?

00:06:14.870 --> 00:06:16.870
Food I saved from the humans.

00:06:16.890 --> 00:06:17.940
It's delicious.

00:06:18.000 --> 00:06:20.000
Especially this sugarcane. Try it.

00:06:21.120 --> 00:06:22.800
It's such an ugly thing.

00:06:23.580 --> 00:06:25.640
Just looking at it kills my appetite.

00:06:35.090 --> 00:06:36.550
What kind of treasure is this?

00:06:36.550 --> 00:06:37.210
Sugarcane.

00:06:37.330 --> 00:06:38.720
And this one's good too.

00:06:44.490 --> 00:06:45.240
Delicious.

00:06:48.950 --> 00:06:49.510
It tastes different.

00:06:49.510 --> 00:06:50.480
Good. It's really good.

00:06:50.480 --> 00:06:51.040
Not bad.

00:06:52.040 --> 00:06:53.040
Try this one.

00:06:53.040 --> 00:06:53.970
Is it delicious?

00:07:10.600 --> 00:07:12.780
Once mighty and proud across the realms,

00:07:12.780 --> 00:07:13.630
the demons have now

00:07:13.630 --> 00:07:15.690
been driven into such a small valley.

00:07:16.550 --> 00:07:18.080
It is truly a pitiful sight.

00:07:28.480 --> 00:07:29.160
Senior.

00:07:30.720 --> 00:07:31.270
Senior.

00:07:31.330 --> 00:07:31.990
Senior.

00:07:32.270 --> 00:07:34.570
Witnessing your power today

00:07:34.830 --> 00:07:35.950
has filled us with awe and admiration.

00:07:35.950 --> 00:07:36.510
Yes, yes.

00:07:37.390 --> 00:07:39.430
We humbly ask
if you would be willing to teach us,

00:07:39.430 --> 00:07:41.070
so that if humans invade again,

00:07:41.070 --> 00:07:42.600
we may be able to assist you.

00:07:42.630 --> 00:07:43.159
Yes.

00:07:48.190 --> 00:07:50.320
If you can still stand after three days

00:07:50.360 --> 00:07:51.720
of training under me,

00:07:52.310 --> 00:07:53.840
I'll teach you some skills.

00:07:55.510 --> 00:07:55.920
Okay.

00:07:56.480 --> 00:07:58.430
1,996.

00:07:58.430 --> 00:08:00.340
1,997.

00:08:00.430 --> 00:08:02.660
1,998.

00:08:02.920 --> 00:08:05.870
1,999.

00:08:05.870 --> 00:08:06.920
2,000!

00:08:10.290 --> 00:08:11.890
Cultivate spiritual power.

00:08:12.190 --> 00:08:13.600
Train your physical body.

00:08:13.600 --> 00:08:14.120
Train!

00:08:14.510 --> 00:08:16.990
Attack, and your strength will double.

00:08:17.240 --> 00:08:19.540
Defend, and you can withstand blows.

00:08:19.920 --> 00:08:20.630
Remember this:

00:08:20.630 --> 00:08:22.600
Might makes right!

00:08:23.190 --> 00:08:25.400
Might makes right!

00:08:25.560 --> 00:08:27.680
Might makes right!

00:08:27.750 --> 00:08:29.870
Might makes right!

00:08:30.040 --> 00:08:32.200
Might makes right!

00:08:32.200 --> 00:08:34.240
Might makes right!

00:08:34.240 --> 00:08:36.360
Might makes right!

00:08:36.390 --> 00:08:38.630
Might makes right!

00:08:38.630 --> 00:08:39.630
You are right!

00:08:39.630 --> 00:08:40.850
You are right!

00:08:40.909 --> 00:08:41.840
Senior.

00:08:44.000 --> 00:08:45.150
This is Bamboo's second uncle.

00:08:45.150 --> 00:08:46.280
I brought it for you.

00:08:48.430 --> 00:08:49.880
Remove the bottom part.

00:09:05.120 --> 00:09:05.480
Done.

00:09:16.670 --> 00:09:18.130
Let me teach you a new game.

00:09:18.410 --> 00:09:19.070
It's called

00:09:19.330 --> 00:09:20.190
Ju.

00:09:22.880 --> 00:09:24.940
Without using spiritual power,

00:09:25.030 --> 00:09:27.030
you must throw the ball

00:09:28.550 --> 00:09:29.880
into that basket to win.

00:09:30.030 --> 00:09:31.120
And if I win?

00:09:32.000 --> 00:09:32.730
If you win...

00:09:33.200 --> 00:09:34.000
if you win,

00:09:34.670 --> 00:09:36.000
I'll grant you one wish.

00:09:45.880 --> 00:09:46.440
Wait.

00:09:47.270 --> 00:09:49.600
I haven't finished explaining the rules.

00:09:49.870 --> 00:09:51.670
I won't use spiritual power either,

00:09:51.670 --> 00:09:52.270
but I'll

00:09:52.350 --> 00:09:53.990
try my best to stop you.

00:09:54.720 --> 00:09:55.840
Are you ready?

00:10:01.840 --> 00:10:02.790
My mother said

00:10:02.790 --> 00:10:04.920
that those who love to laugh are lucky.

00:10:06.360 --> 00:10:07.390
That doesn't count.

00:10:07.390 --> 00:10:07.990
Try again.

00:10:10.750 --> 00:10:11.210
Come on.

00:10:11.670 --> 00:10:12.870
Alright, here I come.

00:10:19.120 --> 00:10:20.440
Again!

00:10:21.080 --> 00:10:21.690
Go!

00:10:42.790 --> 00:10:43.400
Look.

00:10:48.600 --> 00:10:49.690
Amazing.

00:10:55.000 --> 00:10:56.400
I'll spare you this time.

00:10:56.440 --> 00:10:57.700
Go back and tell Hong Ye

00:10:58.080 --> 00:10:59.960
that if he wants to
attempt an assassination,

00:10:59.960 --> 00:11:01.750
he should send more capable people.

00:11:01.750 --> 00:11:02.480
No, no.

00:11:02.910 --> 00:11:04.240
You've misunderstood.

00:11:05.870 --> 00:11:06.960
Well, we...

00:11:07.030 --> 00:11:08.550
We just wanted to learn from

00:11:08.550 --> 00:11:10.080
your extraordinary poise.

00:11:10.080 --> 00:11:10.680
No, I mean—

00:11:11.270 --> 00:11:12.000
your integrity.

00:11:12.000 --> 00:11:12.550
Yes.

00:11:12.550 --> 00:11:13.560
For bamboo,

00:11:13.720 --> 00:11:15.720
integrity is of the utmost importance.

00:11:15.720 --> 00:11:16.550
Yes.

00:11:16.790 --> 00:11:18.150
Whatever you plan to do,

00:11:18.730 --> 00:11:20.760
keep at least ten zhang away from me.

00:11:22.000 --> 00:11:23.410
Do not let Xiao Yao
misunderstand anything.

00:11:23.410 --> 00:11:25.410
Otherwise, I will kill you on sight.

00:11:26.240 --> 00:11:29.360
As long as I stay more than ten zhang away,
I can follow you, right?

00:11:29.360 --> 00:11:30.080
Ten zhang.

00:11:31.360 --> 00:11:33.390
Ten is enough.
I can follow you now, right?

00:11:33.390 --> 00:11:34.200
My Lord!

00:11:34.630 --> 00:11:36.240
My Lord, something terrible has happened!

00:11:36.240 --> 00:11:38.570
You need to do something
about it, My Lord!

00:11:38.630 --> 00:11:39.320
My Lord.

00:11:39.550 --> 00:11:40.550
What's so urgent?

00:11:41.320 --> 00:11:42.510
Those three ancient demons

00:11:42.510 --> 00:11:44.200
are buying loyalty everywhere.

00:11:44.200 --> 00:11:45.600
If this continues,

00:11:45.600 --> 00:11:46.720
all the minor and inexperienced demons

00:11:46.720 --> 00:11:48.450
will fall under their control.

00:11:48.550 --> 00:11:50.270
You're making a fuss over nothing.

00:11:50.270 --> 00:11:51.790
I'm really not.

00:11:51.870 --> 00:11:53.470
Go take a look and you'll see.

00:11:53.670 --> 00:11:54.360
Hurry!

00:11:54.550 --> 00:11:55.600
Let's go, My Lord!

00:11:59.320 --> 00:12:01.450
Whoever can lay so much as a finger on me

00:12:01.890 --> 00:12:04.150
will be granted
a hundred years of cultivation.

00:12:04.150 --> 00:12:04.600
What?

00:12:04.600 --> 00:12:05.120
Really?

00:12:05.120 --> 00:12:05.600
What?

00:12:05.840 --> 00:12:07.480
-A hundred years?
-A hundred years of cultivation?

00:12:07.480 --> 00:12:07.870
A hundred years!

00:12:07.870 --> 00:12:08.440
One,

00:12:08.440 --> 00:12:09.030
two,

00:12:09.030 --> 00:12:09.750
pull!

00:12:11.360 --> 00:12:12.030
My Lord,

00:12:12.270 --> 00:12:13.570
look at them.

00:12:13.720 --> 00:12:14.910
They're supposed to be training,

00:12:14.910 --> 00:12:15.600
yet here they are fooling around

00:12:15.600 --> 00:12:17.200
with this useless nonsense.

00:12:17.790 --> 00:12:18.520
Pull harder!

00:12:18.750 --> 00:12:20.000
I am trying!

00:12:20.720 --> 00:12:21.980
Did you skip your meal?

00:12:22.790 --> 00:12:23.390
Harder!

00:12:24.600 --> 00:12:25.200
Harder!

00:12:25.200 --> 00:12:25.910
One, two,

00:12:25.910 --> 00:12:26.720
pull!

00:12:27.120 --> 00:12:28.830
One, two, pull!

00:12:29.010 --> 00:12:31.040
One, two, pull!

00:12:31.200 --> 00:12:32.900
Training physical strength like this

00:12:32.900 --> 00:12:34.700
isn't such a bad thing after all.

00:12:38.480 --> 00:12:39.370
My Lord.

00:12:42.030 --> 00:12:42.960
Look over there.

00:12:46.870 --> 00:12:47.480
Again!

00:12:59.720 --> 00:13:00.340
Forget it,

00:13:02.440 --> 00:13:03.840
just tell me your wish.

00:13:13.120 --> 00:13:14.910
Since Dali left,

00:13:16.790 --> 00:13:18.720
I haven't had any friends.

00:13:20.720 --> 00:13:22.800
No one wants to play with me.

00:13:22.840 --> 00:13:24.790
I'm unhappy every day.

00:13:29.080 --> 00:13:31.330
But just now,
when I was playing with you, Senior,

00:13:31.330 --> 00:13:33.130
it felt like I had a friend again.

00:13:37.670 --> 00:13:39.150
So let's keep going.

00:13:45.750 --> 00:13:47.510
You said it yourself.

00:13:49.480 --> 00:13:50.030
This time

00:13:52.000 --> 00:13:52.860
it's my turn!

00:14:12.240 --> 00:14:13.440
How can there be

00:14:14.390 --> 00:14:16.930
a demon lord with such overwhelming power?

00:14:17.020 --> 00:14:18.240
Indeed.

00:14:18.870 --> 00:14:22.180
The way he concentrates on
his work is mesmerizing.

00:14:22.270 --> 00:14:23.910
Yes.

00:14:25.060 --> 00:14:27.560
They're clearly old-fashioned
fabric and patterns,

00:14:27.560 --> 00:14:29.030
yet on him

00:14:29.030 --> 00:14:30.590
they look extraordinary.

00:14:33.340 --> 00:14:35.100
You're too young to get it.

00:14:35.600 --> 00:14:37.080
This is called classical style.

00:14:37.080 --> 00:14:38.070
Classical?

00:14:38.320 --> 00:14:39.380
Classical beauty.

00:14:54.150 --> 00:14:54.750
I...

00:14:56.630 --> 00:14:59.290
I never imagined that
after ten thousand years,

00:14:59.410 --> 00:15:00.770
styles could change

00:15:00.840 --> 00:15:01.960
so much.

00:15:02.810 --> 00:15:04.530
Demon Lord, this is my

00:15:04.580 --> 00:15:05.360
hair.

00:15:09.470 --> 00:15:10.800
It looks so beautiful.

00:15:11.790 --> 00:15:12.870
Lift your head.

00:15:14.510 --> 00:15:15.770
Stretch out your arms.

00:15:17.630 --> 00:15:18.480
A bit higher.

00:15:19.950 --> 00:15:21.360
That's beautiful.

00:15:21.430 --> 00:15:22.430
It suits you well.

00:15:24.000 --> 00:15:25.750
Bamboo, he's complimenting you.

00:15:25.750 --> 00:15:26.510
My Lord,

00:15:26.510 --> 00:15:27.240
look at this.

00:15:27.960 --> 00:15:29.720
My Lord, please wait for me.

00:15:29.720 --> 00:15:31.030
My Lord, there's no need to worry.

00:15:31.030 --> 00:15:32.080
Xiao Ming and Xiao Mu

00:15:32.080 --> 00:15:33.860
will always be by your side.

00:15:34.240 --> 00:15:35.750
Your spiritual power
has only just recovered,

00:15:35.750 --> 00:15:37.600
so please make sure to rest more.

00:15:38.360 --> 00:15:40.600
They're just a few ancient demons
from ten thousand years ago.

00:15:40.600 --> 00:15:42.530
What is there for me to worry about?

00:15:43.960 --> 00:15:46.030
Haven't I already seen everything
you wanted to show me?

00:15:46.030 --> 00:15:47.390
Why are you still following me?

00:15:47.390 --> 00:15:47.790
I...

00:15:49.000 --> 00:15:49.840
Why are you here?

00:15:49.840 --> 00:15:50.370
Xiao Yao.

00:15:52.840 --> 00:15:53.960
Take care of yourself, My Lord.

00:15:53.960 --> 00:15:55.000
I came to see you.

00:15:56.510 --> 00:15:57.640
What smells so good?

00:15:58.390 --> 00:15:59.990
I made some flower pastries.

00:16:01.670 --> 00:16:03.610
Ao Hen, Qiong Qi, and Teng She

00:16:03.670 --> 00:16:05.080
did a great job repairing the barrier.

00:16:05.080 --> 00:16:06.670
I want to invite them
to try these flower pastries

00:16:06.670 --> 00:16:07.750
to show my gratitude.

00:16:07.750 --> 00:16:08.670
You came at the right time.

00:16:08.670 --> 00:16:09.730
Let's go find them.

00:16:10.670 --> 00:16:12.400
Those three are ancient beasts

00:16:12.670 --> 00:16:15.130
and can be extremely cruel
when they go wild.

00:16:16.200 --> 00:16:17.440
Well, Xiao Mu once said

00:16:17.440 --> 00:16:19.500
I would bring disaster to the demons.

00:16:21.080 --> 00:16:22.200
I can tell

00:16:22.440 --> 00:16:24.270
they bear no ill will toward the demons.

00:16:24.270 --> 00:16:26.000
But they have feelings for you.

00:16:30.600 --> 00:16:31.510
So,

00:16:31.910 --> 00:16:35.320
are you afraid they'll harm
the demons, or...

00:16:35.320 --> 00:16:35.840
Yes,

00:16:36.270 --> 00:16:37.150
I'm jealous.

00:16:40.680 --> 00:16:41.870
If I hadn't heard it with my own ears,

00:16:41.870 --> 00:16:44.140
I wouldn't believe you'd say that.

00:16:45.630 --> 00:16:46.910
I used to think

00:16:47.640 --> 00:16:49.750
that as long as my spiritual power
was strong enough,

00:16:49.750 --> 00:16:51.200
there was nothing in this world

00:16:51.200 --> 00:16:52.670
I needed to fear.

00:16:54.150 --> 00:16:55.120
But after I met you,

00:16:55.120 --> 00:16:56.080
I realized

00:16:57.390 --> 00:16:59.520
that even the strongest can be afraid.

00:17:00.510 --> 00:17:01.910
I'm afraid of losing you.

00:17:02.390 --> 00:17:04.050
I'm afraid you might get hurt,

00:17:04.069 --> 00:17:06.130
and even more afraid that those three

00:17:07.290 --> 00:17:09.290
might join forces and take you away.

00:17:10.160 --> 00:17:12.020
Even if I fought with all my might,

00:17:12.640 --> 00:17:14.300
I still couldn't get you back.

00:17:38.970 --> 00:17:40.170
Are you still afraid?

00:17:42.350 --> 00:17:42.790
Hmm.

00:17:43.200 --> 00:17:43.720
Yes.

00:17:46.440 --> 00:17:48.030
Alright, let's be serious.

00:17:48.050 --> 00:17:49.980
Come, let's go find them together.

00:17:50.310 --> 00:17:50.840
Let's go.

00:17:55.030 --> 00:17:56.160
Demon Lord,

00:17:56.590 --> 00:17:58.310
those who benefit the demons
deserve rewards,

00:17:58.310 --> 00:18:00.030
and those who harm them
deserve punishment.

00:18:00.030 --> 00:18:01.110
They worked hard

00:18:01.110 --> 00:18:02.440
repairing the barrier.

00:18:03.350 --> 00:18:05.430
They deserve some appreciation.

00:18:09.510 --> 00:18:10.590
Aren't you coming?

00:18:13.270 --> 00:18:14.530
Then I'll go by myself.

00:18:16.270 --> 00:18:16.920
I'm off.

00:18:20.680 --> 00:18:22.080
You're really not going?

00:18:30.000 --> 00:18:31.400
You're really not going?

00:18:50.570 --> 00:18:51.790
Did you make all these?

00:18:51.790 --> 00:18:52.110
Yes.

00:18:52.110 --> 00:18:54.170
Whatever you make must be delicious.

00:19:03.200 --> 00:19:04.720
It's so delicious.

00:19:05.310 --> 00:19:06.030
I declare

00:19:06.310 --> 00:19:07.240
this is the most

00:19:07.240 --> 00:19:08.900
delicious thing in the world.

00:19:13.440 --> 00:19:14.240
Ao Hen,

00:19:14.510 --> 00:19:16.440
These flower pastries
won't last for ten thousand years.

00:19:16.440 --> 00:19:18.310
Don't tell me you want to
plant them in the ground

00:19:18.310 --> 00:19:19.440
so they'll grow into
flower trees next year.

00:19:19.440 --> 00:19:20.400
What do you know?

00:19:20.400 --> 00:19:22.240
These flower pastries
were made by Xiao Yao,

00:19:22.240 --> 00:19:23.400
so of course I need to keep them

00:19:23.400 --> 00:19:24.730
to enjoy them properly.

00:19:26.210 --> 00:19:29.030
-Enjoy them properly.
-To thank the three of you
for your hard work,

00:19:29.030 --> 00:19:31.760
these flower pastries
were made by me and Hong Ye.

00:19:35.550 --> 00:19:36.310
Hong Ye,

00:19:36.520 --> 00:19:37.850
come out and eat with us.

00:19:45.140 --> 00:19:48.270
Do you really think I'll come
just because you called me?

00:20:01.680 --> 00:20:03.960
No matter what grievances
we've had before,

00:20:03.960 --> 00:20:05.680
we demons are one family.

00:20:05.920 --> 00:20:07.450
I offer tea instead of wine,

00:20:07.590 --> 00:20:10.250
and consider
our misunderstandings resolved.

00:20:28.850 --> 00:20:29.780
Go ahead and eat.

00:20:35.080 --> 00:20:36.050
This is mine.

00:20:39.030 --> 00:20:40.240
You're not worthy

00:20:40.750 --> 00:20:41.810
of sharing with us.

00:20:45.360 --> 00:20:47.000
My sister worked hard to make these.

00:20:47.000 --> 00:20:47.750
Don't you dare

00:20:47.750 --> 00:20:48.830
ruin them.

00:20:49.830 --> 00:20:51.470
You've already eaten so much.
You're still eating?

00:20:51.470 --> 00:20:52.830
Sister likes watching me eat.

00:20:52.830 --> 00:20:54.880
She already told you
not to call her "Sister" anymore.

00:20:54.880 --> 00:20:55.750
I'll call her whatever I want.

00:20:55.750 --> 00:20:58.030
It's none of your business, you big oaf.

00:20:58.790 --> 00:20:59.540
Teng She,

00:20:59.720 --> 00:21:02.160
don't think I don't see through
your little schemes.

00:21:02.160 --> 00:21:04.890
Stop hiding behind the
brother-and-sister act.

00:21:05.160 --> 00:21:06.440
You're always the most scheming one,

00:21:06.440 --> 00:21:08.550
and you've got the nerve
to say that about me?

00:21:08.550 --> 00:21:09.200
Hong Ye,

00:21:09.800 --> 00:21:11.200
this is all because of you.

00:21:11.200 --> 00:21:11.930
Let go.

00:21:20.440 --> 00:21:21.220
I said

00:21:21.310 --> 00:21:22.550
I'd be the one to kill Hong Ye.

00:21:22.550 --> 00:21:23.550
Everyone, let go!

00:21:34.030 --> 00:21:35.440
All of you stop!

00:21:44.070 --> 00:21:45.730
-Sister.
-Don't call me that.

00:21:46.480 --> 00:21:47.820
Aren't you all tired?

00:21:48.550 --> 00:21:49.200
Xiao Yao,

00:21:49.270 --> 00:21:50.510
I've never forced you

00:21:51.110 --> 00:21:52.970
to do anything you didn't want to.

00:21:53.240 --> 00:21:53.920
But today, when I saw you

00:21:53.920 --> 00:21:55.850
look at him with such infatuation,

00:21:56.000 --> 00:21:57.400
I just couldn't stand it.

00:21:58.270 --> 00:21:59.440
Since we met,

00:22:00.440 --> 00:22:02.310
you've acted like
you don't know us at all,

00:22:02.310 --> 00:22:04.440
only desperately protecting Hong Ye.

00:22:04.720 --> 00:22:06.770
Aren't you curious about your past?

00:22:08.070 --> 00:22:09.060
Don't you want to ask

00:22:09.060 --> 00:22:10.640
why we just came out of Yunmeng Lake

00:22:10.640 --> 00:22:12.790
and immediately wanted to
settle scores with him?

00:22:12.790 --> 00:22:14.160
I truly don't understand

00:22:14.160 --> 00:22:15.960
whether you genuinely don't know,

00:22:15.960 --> 00:22:17.920
or if you're pretending
not to know just so you can stay with him.

00:22:17.920 --> 00:22:19.900
I don't want to know about the past.

00:22:20.200 --> 00:22:21.830
Ten thousand years have passed.

00:22:21.830 --> 00:22:22.750
The world

00:22:22.920 --> 00:22:24.070
has already changed.

00:22:24.070 --> 00:22:25.680
How could I not have changed?

00:22:26.590 --> 00:22:27.110
You...

00:22:27.590 --> 00:22:28.110
Yes,

00:22:28.310 --> 00:22:30.000
it's been over ten thousand years,

00:22:30.000 --> 00:22:31.830
but your personality
hasn't changed at all.

00:22:31.830 --> 00:22:32.640
How do you explain that?

00:22:32.640 --> 00:22:33.750
Doesn't that prove

00:22:34.230 --> 00:22:36.230
that my choice won't change either?

00:22:42.920 --> 00:22:43.910
I was hoping

00:22:44.350 --> 00:22:46.000
to have a proper conversation
with you all.

00:22:46.000 --> 00:22:47.030
But now I see

00:22:47.030 --> 00:22:49.090
there's no point in talking further.

00:22:51.070 --> 00:22:52.200
Tonight is the night

00:22:52.350 --> 00:22:54.810
Xiao Yao and I
will consummate our marriage.

00:22:55.410 --> 00:22:56.980
Consummate your marriage?

00:22:57.460 --> 00:22:59.790
No matter what we went through
in the past,

00:23:01.680 --> 00:23:03.810
she is the woman I will marry in the end.

00:23:04.880 --> 00:23:05.510
When did

00:23:06.680 --> 00:23:07.810
you two get married?

00:23:09.270 --> 00:23:10.400
A hundred years ago.

00:23:13.710 --> 00:23:14.960
No matter how much time passes,

00:23:14.960 --> 00:23:16.520
no matter what we go through,

00:23:16.520 --> 00:23:17.820
the man I will marry

00:23:18.110 --> 00:23:19.110
is Hong Ye.

00:23:34.310 --> 00:23:37.250
I waited for you in Yunmeng Lake
for ten thousand years.

00:23:37.250 --> 00:23:38.450
Why couldn't you wait

00:23:39.190 --> 00:23:40.630
even a mere hundred?

00:23:42.890 --> 00:23:44.510
Then let today's flower pastries

00:23:44.510 --> 00:23:46.670
serve as our wedding pastries.

00:23:46.960 --> 00:23:48.790
Since the three of you
have already eaten them,

00:23:48.790 --> 00:23:51.480
don't bring up what happened
ten thousand years ago again.

00:23:51.480 --> 00:23:52.400
Let us go,

00:23:52.400 --> 00:23:54.060
and spare yourselves as well.

00:23:54.920 --> 00:23:56.180
Wedding pastries?

00:23:59.640 --> 00:24:00.210
Pah!

00:24:01.110 --> 00:24:02.270
Filthy things!

00:24:03.960 --> 00:24:04.440
I...

00:24:04.590 --> 00:24:05.160
Pah!

00:24:05.590 --> 00:24:06.650
Wedding pastries?

00:24:11.510 --> 00:24:13.370
The mortal world is truly filthy.

00:24:15.240 --> 00:24:16.790
It's only been a few days,

00:24:19.480 --> 00:24:21.410
and I already have lines on my face.

00:24:21.550 --> 00:24:22.310
Not at all,

00:24:22.680 --> 00:24:23.740
Exalted Immortal.

00:24:24.000 --> 00:24:25.240
Your skin is as smooth as jade,

00:24:25.240 --> 00:24:26.480
and your flesh is like ice and bone.

00:24:26.480 --> 00:24:28.210
Even my fingertips slip

00:24:28.400 --> 00:24:29.930
slip when I touch your skin.

00:24:31.110 --> 00:24:32.710
If the war were not so urgent,

00:24:34.510 --> 00:24:36.110
what reason would there be

00:24:39.000 --> 00:24:40.860
to linger in such a tainted place?

00:24:41.960 --> 00:24:42.640
Yes.

00:24:43.510 --> 00:24:44.790
His Majesty and all the consorts

00:24:44.790 --> 00:24:47.270
are deeply grateful
for your great kindness.

00:24:47.270 --> 00:24:48.640
The consorts of every palace

00:24:48.640 --> 00:24:50.680
have offered up their
personal cosmetics and adornments.

00:24:50.680 --> 00:24:52.610
Please, choose whatever you like.

00:25:17.030 --> 00:25:18.080
I deserve death,

00:25:18.110 --> 00:25:19.370
yet I beg you for mercy.

00:25:19.720 --> 00:25:21.920
Just now, I was truly frightened.

00:25:22.070 --> 00:25:23.830
The person who prepared
this box of hairpins

00:25:23.830 --> 00:25:25.240
is extremely malicious.

00:25:25.680 --> 00:25:27.550
You must not use these, Exalted Immortal.

00:25:27.550 --> 00:25:28.590
The designs

00:25:28.590 --> 00:25:29.680
of these hairpins

00:25:29.680 --> 00:25:30.640
are based on

00:25:31.000 --> 00:25:31.920
the phoenix tail,

00:25:31.920 --> 00:25:32.750
silk orchids,

00:25:33.110 --> 00:25:34.270
and dragon's blood flowers—

00:25:34.270 --> 00:25:35.870
all symbolizing longevity.

00:25:35.920 --> 00:25:38.380
Only elders of advanced age
would wear them.

00:25:38.400 --> 00:25:39.830
You are merely sixteen,

00:25:40.110 --> 00:25:41.310
in the prime of youth.

00:25:41.310 --> 00:25:42.570
To display such things

00:25:44.030 --> 00:25:45.160
is truly...

00:25:47.480 --> 00:25:48.550
Which consort

00:25:49.270 --> 00:25:51.110
sent this dressing case?

00:25:51.720 --> 00:25:53.750
The Exalted Immortal is speaking to you.

00:25:53.750 --> 00:25:54.880
The Western Palace.

00:25:55.350 --> 00:25:59.030
Was it the Consort of the Western Palace
herself who prepared this dressing case?

00:25:59.030 --> 00:26:00.720
I truly don't know.

00:26:00.920 --> 00:26:03.510
The Emperor always praises
the Consort of the Western Palace for her wisdom.

00:26:03.510 --> 00:26:04.830
All matters in the inner palace,

00:26:04.830 --> 00:26:05.880
great and small,

00:26:05.880 --> 00:26:08.060
are decided by her alone.

00:26:08.790 --> 00:26:10.300
Surely it was an unintentional oversight

00:26:10.300 --> 00:26:11.790
on her part.

00:26:12.030 --> 00:26:13.160
Exalted Immortal, I beg you

00:26:13.160 --> 00:26:14.310
to show leniency,

00:26:14.310 --> 00:26:15.860
considering the Consort's

00:26:16.030 --> 00:26:17.550
unparalleled beauty and grace.

00:26:17.550 --> 00:26:19.350
Unparalleled beauty and grace?

00:26:23.720 --> 00:26:25.580
Is she truly that stunning?

00:26:25.880 --> 00:26:27.940
Of course, she cannot compare to you.

00:26:28.160 --> 00:26:30.090
But within the Tiansheng Kingdom,

00:26:30.310 --> 00:26:32.170
the Consort of the Western Palace

00:26:32.430 --> 00:26:34.720
is indeed regarded as foremost in beauty.

00:26:34.720 --> 00:26:35.660
Yanlan,

00:26:37.720 --> 00:26:39.320
which palace do you serve in?

00:26:41.520 --> 00:26:42.400
I

00:26:43.790 --> 00:26:45.650
have served in the Eastern Palace

00:26:46.060 --> 00:26:47.440
since childhood.

00:26:51.350 --> 00:26:54.790
At this critical juncture
of life and death for the nation,

00:26:55.820 --> 00:26:56.680
how dare you drag me into

00:26:56.680 --> 00:26:58.610
the intrigues of the inner palace?

00:27:03.340 --> 00:27:05.100
Tell your master

00:27:06.730 --> 00:27:08.190
to give me an explanation!

00:27:09.270 --> 00:27:09.940
Exalted Immortal,

00:27:09.940 --> 00:27:11.070
I'm clumsy with words

00:27:11.070 --> 00:27:12.000
and slow-witted,

00:27:12.000 --> 00:27:13.140
and I have offended you.

00:27:13.140 --> 00:27:14.480
But this matter truly has nothing to do

00:27:14.480 --> 00:27:15.640
with my lady.

00:27:16.220 --> 00:27:18.420
Please be merciful, Exalted Immortal.

00:27:50.240 --> 00:27:51.500
I spoke carelessly

00:27:51.610 --> 00:27:53.540
and angered the Exalted Immortal.

00:27:54.280 --> 00:27:56.210
will punish myself to appease you.

00:28:19.170 --> 00:28:20.370
All of you, withdraw.

00:28:33.750 --> 00:28:35.440
Who have you truly become now?

