00:31:36.720 --> 00:31:41.060
♪ Like the red thread strung together,
hanging on a sharp sword ♪

00:31:42.120 --> 00:31:44.870
♪ Waiting for the heartbeat
to shatter time ♪

00:31:45.940 --> 00:31:47.440
♪ The chains of fate ♪

00:31:48.400 --> 00:31:52.180
♪ Belong to us, in the blink of an eye,
it's 1,000 years ♪

00:31:52.930 --> 00:31:56.690
♪ You and I meet across mountains
and rivers, under the bright moon ♪

00:31:57.540 --> 00:31:59.000
♪ The obsession that rises like magpies ♪

00:32:00.070 --> 00:32:01.580
♪ Both flushing ♪

00:32:02.520 --> 00:32:06.130
♪ Waiting to walk hand in hand
through the chessboard of fate ♪

00:32:07.060 --> 00:32:09.080
♪ The carefree moments that belong to us ♪

00:32:09.080 --> 00:32:11.280
Why is this fragment of the mirror here?

00:32:12.710 --> 00:32:14.770
This piece is "Love and Separation."

00:32:15.520 --> 00:32:17.070
♪ Moments ♪

00:32:17.070 --> 00:32:20.530
The obsession that has lingered
in my heart for a hundred years

00:32:20.900 --> 00:32:22.560
has finally been laid to rest.

00:32:28.160 --> 00:32:30.220
All that has passed is but a prologue.

00:32:31.310 --> 00:32:33.240
From now on, we will stay together,

00:32:33.880 --> 00:32:34.750
never to part.

00:33:00.590 --> 00:33:01.390
What's wrong?

00:33:02.310 --> 00:33:03.480
Did you hear something?

00:33:03.480 --> 00:33:05.110
You're stepping on my foot!

00:33:05.200 --> 00:33:06.060
Move over a bit.

00:33:10.240 --> 00:33:10.960
Be quiet.

00:33:10.990 --> 00:33:11.590
Let me listen.

00:33:11.590 --> 00:33:12.390
Don't push me.

00:33:13.070 --> 00:33:13.440
I...

00:33:19.030 --> 00:33:20.090
What are you doing?

00:33:22.310 --> 00:33:22.880
Hurry!

00:33:24.590 --> 00:33:25.200
What are you doing?

00:33:25.200 --> 00:33:26.110
I'm eavesdropping.

00:33:26.110 --> 00:33:26.920
Does it sound good?

00:33:26.920 --> 00:33:27.750
Yes, it is!

00:33:27.750 --> 00:33:28.240
Do you enjoy it?

00:33:28.240 --> 00:33:28.880
I love it!

00:33:28.880 --> 00:33:29.590
Are you still listening?

00:33:29.590 --> 00:33:30.310
Of course!

00:33:30.310 --> 00:33:31.310
Let me listen too.

00:33:39.400 --> 00:33:40.060
How stupid.

00:33:41.750 --> 00:33:42.550
Are you smart?

00:33:43.240 --> 00:33:44.100
Thank you, Sir.

00:34:00.400 --> 00:34:00.800
No way.

00:34:01.400 --> 00:34:02.860
How could I do such a thing?

00:34:03.030 --> 00:34:03.680
Honestly!

00:34:09.230 --> 00:34:10.630
Don't feel bad about it.

00:34:11.150 --> 00:34:11.860
Let me tell you,

00:34:11.860 --> 00:34:14.230
whether it's eavesdropping or peeping,

00:34:14.400 --> 00:34:16.070
we should wait outside for His Lordship

00:34:16.070 --> 00:34:17.670
for such an important event.

00:34:18.070 --> 00:34:18.920
Do you agree?

00:34:41.520 --> 00:34:43.780
I never thought they'd still be together

00:34:45.550 --> 00:34:47.280
even after ten thousand years.

00:34:50.190 --> 00:34:51.159
So,

00:34:51.280 --> 00:34:53.550
why are we still here

00:34:54.320 --> 00:34:55.150
anyway?

00:34:57.650 --> 00:34:59.050
What's the use of crying?

00:35:00.480 --> 00:35:01.880
If she sees you like this,

00:35:03.250 --> 00:35:04.850
she'll only despise you more

00:35:05.400 --> 00:35:07.200
and drift further away from you.

00:35:13.760 --> 00:35:14.510
Hong Ye,

00:35:14.920 --> 00:35:16.370
you coward!

00:35:16.710 --> 00:35:19.820
-You don't even dare to fight me head-on.
-You fought a lot.

00:35:19.820 --> 00:35:20.880
Did Sister ever say

00:35:20.920 --> 00:35:22.760
she'd like you if you won?

00:35:23.280 --> 00:35:24.710
Even if she doesn't like me,

00:35:24.710 --> 00:35:26.910
I can't let that Hong Ye take advantage.

00:35:27.880 --> 00:35:29.210
I can't let him have her.

00:35:31.360 --> 00:35:32.290
Get out of my way.

00:35:33.960 --> 00:35:34.480
Move!

00:35:34.480 --> 00:35:36.280
You're going to pick a fight with Hong Ye?

00:35:36.280 --> 00:35:36.930
Of course.

00:35:36.960 --> 00:35:38.450
They're already married.

00:35:38.760 --> 00:35:39.920
If you hurt Hong Ye now,

00:35:39.920 --> 00:35:41.030
you're hurting Sister.

00:35:41.030 --> 00:35:42.780
I won't allow you to hurt her!

00:35:43.760 --> 00:35:44.400
Teng She,

00:35:45.190 --> 00:35:46.760
whose side are you on?

00:35:46.790 --> 00:35:47.990
I'm on Sister's side.

00:35:49.360 --> 00:35:50.620
As long as she's happy,

00:35:51.030 --> 00:35:52.560
even if it breaks my heart,

00:35:53.760 --> 00:35:55.820
I'll protect her choice till the end.

00:35:57.590 --> 00:35:59.620
What if Hong Ye's affection is just

00:35:59.880 --> 00:36:01.960
as false as it was ten millennia ago,

00:36:01.960 --> 00:36:04.020
and his motives are just as ulterior?

00:36:06.230 --> 00:36:08.150
Are you truly willing to stand by

00:36:08.730 --> 00:36:10.530
and watch her be betrayed again?

00:36:12.230 --> 00:36:13.510
If Xiao Yao knew

00:36:13.510 --> 00:36:16.170
what Hong Ye truly did to her
all those years ago,

00:36:16.280 --> 00:36:18.540
she would never have agreed to marry him.

00:36:21.230 --> 00:36:22.040
Gentlemen,

00:36:22.190 --> 00:36:23.820
if we truly care for her,

00:36:24.030 --> 00:36:25.890
the most important thing we can do

00:36:26.320 --> 00:36:28.860
is to reveal Hong Ye's true nature—

00:36:29.320 --> 00:36:30.880
to let her see it clearly
and make her own choice again.

00:36:30.880 --> 00:36:32.400
It's not that simple.

00:36:32.670 --> 00:36:33.920
No matter what we say now,

00:36:33.920 --> 00:36:35.280
Sister doesn't want to listen

00:36:35.280 --> 00:36:36.080
or believe us.

00:36:37.480 --> 00:36:38.340
Then let us form

00:36:39.510 --> 00:36:41.380
a Time-Reversal Array.

00:36:42.280 --> 00:36:44.280
That's exactly what I was thinking.

00:37:05.880 --> 00:37:08.090
♪ The Three-Life Stone cracks,
unleashing the light of three lifetimes ♪

00:37:09.690 --> 00:37:11.620
♪ Shattering the window of
the mortal world ♪

00:37:13.160 --> 00:37:15.270
♪ The unity knot loosens,
unlocking the lock of togetherness ♪

00:37:16.690 --> 00:37:18.260
♪ Tasting the scalding flow of life ♪

00:37:19.620 --> 00:37:22.680
♪ Moss traces creep along
the corridor of reincarnation ♪

00:37:24.050 --> 00:37:25.350
♪ The door ring echoes ♪

00:37:26.840 --> 00:37:28.040
♪ The River of Forgetfulness
flows backward ♪

00:37:29.210 --> 00:37:32.200
♪ Streaming across your eyes ♪

00:37:32.360 --> 00:37:33.640
The seasonings aren't fully stocked,

00:37:33.640 --> 00:37:34.320
♪ The tides push the waves ♪

00:37:34.320 --> 00:37:36.330
and the flour isn't as good as the kind
from Pingjiang Prefecture.

00:37:36.330 --> 00:37:36.410
It's the best I can do for now.

00:37:36.410 --> 00:37:37.550
♪ The rings of years keep growing ♪

00:37:37.550 --> 00:37:38.540
Go ahead, have a taste.

00:37:38.540 --> 00:37:40.070
♪ The heart knocks with
the weight of time ♪

00:37:40.820 --> 00:37:42.390
♪ The hair starts to turn grey ♪

00:37:43.460 --> 00:37:46.570
♪ Frost forms on the brow bones ♪

00:37:48.460 --> 00:37:49.620
♪ Flames of the burning heart
cook the fragrance of a bygone world ♪

00:37:49.620 --> 00:37:50.350
How is it?

00:37:52.870 --> 00:37:53.670
♪ Dreams break like begonia blossoms ♪

00:37:53.670 --> 00:37:54.840
This is the third best bowl of noodles

00:37:54.840 --> 00:37:55.700
I've ever had.

00:37:55.700 --> 00:37:57.540
♪ Rising against the torrent ♪

00:37:57.540 --> 00:37:58.520
And what about the second best?

00:37:58.520 --> 00:37:59.440
♪ Turning the account of impermanence ♪

00:37:59.440 --> 00:38:00.930
That would be the bowl

00:38:01.480 --> 00:38:03.340
from Xu's Noodles on my birthday.

00:38:03.590 --> 00:38:04.110
So,

00:38:04.760 --> 00:38:06.220
what's the very best then?

00:38:08.190 --> 00:38:09.590
The very best

00:38:09.590 --> 00:38:10.320
will be

00:38:12.070 --> 00:38:14.030
the bowl you make for me tomorrow.

00:38:18.650 --> 00:38:20.220
Oh, so you want me

00:38:20.510 --> 00:38:22.400
to make noodles for you for a lifetime.

00:38:22.400 --> 00:38:22.840
Yes.

00:38:26.360 --> 00:38:28.490
Where did you learn these sweet words?

00:38:30.070 --> 00:38:31.330
Do I need to learn this?

00:38:32.980 --> 00:38:34.980
You're the one who doesn't know how.

00:38:35.630 --> 00:38:36.360
My Lord!

00:38:36.670 --> 00:38:38.110
My Lord, something terrible has happened!

00:38:38.110 --> 00:38:39.800
Three great demons
have occupied Youning Cave.

00:38:39.800 --> 00:38:40.840
They're casting spells
and forming arrays inside,

00:38:40.840 --> 00:38:43.500
saying they want to
settle scores with Xiao Yao.

00:38:52.740 --> 00:38:54.050
Time-Reversal Array.

00:38:56.960 --> 00:38:58.070
What are you doing?